---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations, useTranslatedPath } from '../../i18n/utils';
import { Sparkles, BookOpen, Anchor, Map, Ship } from 'lucide-astro';

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = useTranslations(lang);
const translatePath = useTranslatedPath(lang);

const title = lang === 'zh' ? '岛屿故事 — 传承与陪伴' : 'Island Story — Heritage & Companionship';
const description = lang === 'zh'
  ? '探索 Captain Tort 与小灰的七年远航纪事。'
  : 'Explore the seven-year voyage of Captain Tort and Lil Grey.';

const years = [
  {
    id: 'y1',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y1「启航」' : 'Y1 "The Voyage Begins"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你不是一个人出发的' : 'You are not starting alone',
    image: '/images/drawables/chapter_y1_prologue.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“你会的。我早就知道你会的。”'
      : '"You will do it. I always knew you would."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '出发那天，Captain Tort 走进了海里。这是他最后一次下水，也是小灰第一次出发。三十个故事，三十颗星纹，记忆从此苏醒。'
      : 'The day they set out, Captain Tort walked into the sea. It was his last time in the water, and Lil Grey\'s first departure. Thirty stories, thirty stars, memories awakened.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y2',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y2「远潮」' : 'Y2 "Distant Tides"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '迷路是走进了没有名字的地方' : 'Getting lost is finding the unnamed',
    image: '/images/drawables/route_mistedge_entry.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“雾里找到的东西，不一样。”'
      : '"Things found in the mist are different."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '小灰走进了一条没有名字的路。在那片没有被地图标注的海域，他看见了年轻时的 Captain Tort，理解了什么是真正的传承。'
      : 'Lil Grey walked a road without a name. In those uncharted waters, he saw a young Captain Tort and understood the true meaning of heritage.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y3',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y3「回响」' : 'Y3 "The Echo"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '你知道有人在，所以敢往前走' : 'You dare to move forward knowing they are there',
    image: '/images/drawables/spineback_tree_spring.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“岛记得每一只走过的小海龟。”'
      : '"The island remembers every little tortoise."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '龟脊树长出了第一片叶子。小灰开始自己选择方向，因为他知道，无论走到哪里，岛始终在那里，船长始终在身后。'
      : 'The Spineback Tree grew its first leaf. Lil Grey began choosing his own paths, knowing the island and the Captain were always behind him.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y4',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y4「沉钟」' : 'Y4 "The Sunken Bell"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '越深的地方，越有光在等着' : 'The deeper you go, the more light waits',
    image: '/images/drawables/bell_bellwell_deep.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“最深的地方，也有人留过灯。”'
      : '"Even in the deepest abyss, someone left a light."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '下潜，直到光芒消失。在万年沉寂的深渊，小灰找到了那盏灯，并让沉寂已久的古钟再次震动整片海洋。'
      : 'Diving until the light vanished. In the eternal silence of the abyss, Lil Grey found the lamp and made the ancient bell resonate through the ocean.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y5',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y5「古龟族」' : 'Y5 "The Ancient Kin"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '旧的东西，在新人手里才有重量' : 'Old things gain weight in new hands',
    image: '/images/drawables/old_star_keepers_silhouettes.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“你是一段很长的故事的一部分。”'
      : '"You are part of a very long story."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '七位先祖的影子显现，留下一张残缺的星图。一段被遗忘的历史在小灰手中重新连接，他不再只是他自己，他是历史的延续。'
      : 'Silhouettes of seven ancestors appeared, leaving a fragmented star map. A forgotten history reconnected in Lil Grey\'s hands; he was no longer just himself.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y6',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y6「守岛」' : 'Y6 "Guardian"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '知道如何看着另一个人' : 'Knowing how to watch over another',
    image: '/images/drawables/lil_tan_awake.webp',
    color: 'deep-cyan',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“你已经不需要问我了。”'
      : '"You don\'t need to ask me anymore."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '小棕漂流而至。小灰看着他，用了一个熟悉的眼神——那是 Captain Tort 当年看他的眼神。陪伴者，终成引路人。'
      : 'Lil Tan drifted ashore. Lil Grey watched over him with a familiar gaze — the same one Captain Tort once gave him. The companion became the guide.'
  },
  {
    id: 'y7',
    title: lang === 'zh' ? 'Y7「黎明」' : 'Y7 "The Dawn"',
    subtitle: lang === 'zh' ? '出门散个步，灯塔交给你了' : 'Going for a walk, the lighthouse is yours',
    image: '/images/drawables/three_turtles_lighthouse.webp',
    color: 'tide-gold',
    quote: lang === 'zh'
      ? '“灯塔的灯，现在是你的了。”'
      : '"The lighthouse lamp is yours now."',
    content: lang === 'zh'
      ? '雾彻底散了。船长留下一封简短的信，走向了大海深处。小灰点亮了灯塔，海面上不再有时之雾，只有永恒的光。'
      : 'The mist cleared completely. Leaving a brief note, the Captain walked into the deep. Lil Grey lit the lighthouse; the Time Mist was gone, replaced by eternal light.'
  }
];
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Background Light Glow (Aligned with Gallery/Index) -->
  <div class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full h-full -z-10 pointer-events-none opacity-40">
     <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-tide-gold/10 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
     <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-deep-cyan/10 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 md:py-40">
    <!-- Story Header -->
    <header class="text-center mb-32 space-y-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 glass px-6 py-2 rounded-2xl text-brand-blue text-sm font-black tracking-widest uppercase">
        <BookOpen size={18} />
        <span>{lang === 'zh' ? '远航纪事' : 'THE CHRONICLES'}</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tighter leading-[1.1]">
        {lang === 'zh' ? '传承与' : 'HERITAGE &'}<br />
        <span class="text-gradient-narrative">{lang === 'zh' ? '陪伴的海洋' : 'COMPANIONSHIP'}</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed">
        {lang === 'zh'
          ? '“有人一直看着你，一直关注着你。你只管去面对。我们知道你，相信你，并且会指引你。”'
          : '"Someone is always watching you, always caring. Just face it. We know you, we believe in you, and we will guide you."'
        }
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- The Seven Years Timeline -->
    <div class="relative space-y-40">
      <!-- Vertical Line -->
      <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-tide-gold/20 to-transparent hidden md:block"></div>

      {years.map((year, index) => (
        <div class={`relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 md:gap-24 ${index % 2 === 1 ? 'md:flex-row-reverse' : ''}`}>
          <!-- Year Content -->
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-center md:text-left">
            <div class={`inline-block px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-black tracking-widest uppercase ${year.color === 'tide-gold' ? 'bg-tide-gold/20 text-tide-gold' : 'bg-deep-cyan/20 text-deep-cyan'}`}>
              {year.title}
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">{year.subtitle}</h2>
            <blockquote class={`text-lg md:text-xl italic text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 border-l-4 pl-6 py-2 my-4 ${year.color === 'tide-gold' ? 'border-tide-gold/40' : 'border-deep-cyan/40'}`}>
              {year.quote}
            </blockquote>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed font-medium">
              {year.content}
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Year Image Container -->
          <div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-md">
            <div class="relative group">
              <div class={`absolute -inset-4 blur-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-700 ${year.color === 'tide-gold' ? 'bg-tide-gold/20' : 'bg-deep-cyan/20'}`}></div>
              <div class="glass p-3 rounded-[3rem] border-2 border-white/20 dark:border-white/10 shadow-2xl relative z-10 overflow-hidden transform group-hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-500">
                <img src={year.image} alt={year.title} class="w-full h-auto rounded-[2.2rem] fade-mask" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-white/10 dark:from-black/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- Indicator Dot -->
              <div class={`absolute top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-4 border-white dark:border-[#050b1d] shadow-lg hidden md:block z-20 ${index % 2 === 0 ? '-right-[5.5rem]' : '-left-[5.5rem]'} ${year.color === 'tide-gold' ? 'bg-tide-gold' : 'bg-deep-cyan'}`}></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="mt-60 text-center space-y-12">
      <div class="relative inline-block">
        <div class="absolute -inset-20 bg-brand-blue/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
        <img src="/images/drawables/island_awakened.webp" alt="Island Awakened" class="relative w-64 h-64 mx-auto animate-float drop-shadow-2xl" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        {lang === 'zh' ? '这不是结束' : 'THIS IS NOT THE END'}
      </h3>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium">
        {lang === 'zh'
          ? '这是传承完成的那一刻。灯塔的灯由你点亮，海面上不再有时之雾。'
          : 'It is the moment inheritance is complete. The lighthouse lamp is lit by you, and the Time Mist is gone.'
        }
      </p>
      <div class="pt-8">
        <a href={translatePath('/docs/public/01-gentle-guidance-philosophy')} class="px-12 py-6 bg-brand-blue text-white rounded-[2.5rem] font-black text-xl shadow-2xl shadow-brand-blue/30 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-4">
          <Ship size={24} />
          {lang === 'zh' ? '深入了解技术哲学' : 'DIVE INTO PHILOSOPHY'}
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .text-gradient-narrative {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #E8C77A, #818cf8, #4F8BAB);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
  }
</style>
